dcterms:description: Camelyon16 is a public dataset proposed for metastasis detection in breast cancer, consisting of 271 training images and 129 testing images, yielding roughly 3.2 million patches at 20× magnification and 0.25 million patches at 5× magnification.
dcterms:title: Camelyon16

dcterms:description: The TCGA lung cancer dataset includes WSIs of lung cancer sub-types, consisting of 1054 diagnostic digital slides, with only slide-level labels available.
dcterms:title: TCGA lung cancer
